# Changelog

## 2026-01-25 - Migrate from credentials.json to 1Password

### Changed
- Updated Step 5 credential options to prioritize 1Password (Recommended) over deprecated credentials.json
- Replaced "API Key" option with "1Password Secret (Recommended)" and "Environment Variable" options
- Updated OAuth description to clarify token storage location (~/.claude-oauth/)
- Updated Step 6 credential configuration instructions to provide 1Password and environment variable patterns
- Removed credentials.json instructions

### Added
- references/example-configurations.md: New "1Password Configuration (Recommended)" section at top with:
  - Step-by-step 1Password serviceItems configuration
  - 1Password vault item creation instructions
  - Async client pattern usage example
  - Migration guide from credentials.json to 1Password
- references/error-handling.md: New "1Password Credential Errors" section with:
  - 'not_configured' error handling
  - 'auth_required' error handling (biometric authentication)

### Verification
- ✅ SKILL.md: 359 lines (< 500 limit)
- ✅ command-configurations.md: 143 lines (< 400 limit)
- ✅ error-handling.md: 308 lines (< 400 limit)
- ✅ example-configurations.md: 252 lines (< 400 limit)
- ✅ No remaining references to credentials.json as primary pattern
- ✅ 1Password shown as recommended option
